〈'''随它吧'''〉（{{Lang-en|"Let It Go"}}）是[[迪士尼|迪士尼]]2013年动画电影《[[冰雪奇缘|冰雪奇缘]]》中的一首歌曲，由[[克里斯汀·安德生-洛佩兹|克里斯汀·安德生-洛佩兹]]和[[罗伯特·洛佩兹|罗伯特·洛佩兹]]夫妻两人共同创作词曲。这首歌的片中版本是由为[[艾莎_(迪士尼)|艾莎]]配音的美国演员和歌手[[伊迪娜·曼佐|伊迪娜·门泽尔]]演唱。歌曲后来作为单曲发行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/189112-Listen-to-Club-Remixes-of-Frozen-Single-Let-It-Go-from-Dave-Aud-Paperchaer-and-More-Audio|title=Listen to Club Remixes of "Frozen" Single "Let It Go" from Dave Audé, Papercha$er and More (Audio)|date=March 21, 2014|work=Playbill|access-date=July 1, 2014|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716211625/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/189112-Listen-to-Club-Remixes-of-Frozen-Single-Let-It-Go-from-Dave-Aud-Paperchaer-and-More-Audio|archive-date=July 16, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/code/5944616/idina-menzel-let-it-go-paperchaser-club-remix-exclusive-dance-track|title=Idina Menzel, 'Let It Go' (Papercha$er Club Remix): Exclusive Dance Track Premiere|date=March 20, 2014|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|access-date=July 1, 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706020841/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/code/5944616/idina-menzel-let-it-go-paperchaser-club-remix-exclusive-dance-track|archive-date=July 6, 2014}}</ref>，于2014年1月被[[华特迪士尼唱片|华特迪士尼唱片]]派往[[成人当代音乐|成人当代]]电台<ref>{{cite web|title='Frozen' - The No. 1 Album That's Been Ignored by Radio|url=https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/radio/5876982/frozen-the-no-1-album-thats-been-ignored-by-radio|access-date=June 3, 2014|date=January 20, 2014|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711105717/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/radio/5876982/frozen-the-no-1-album-thats-been-ignored-by-radio|archive-date=July 11, 2014|quote=That's partly owed to how none of the album's songs were promoted to radio outlets until two weeks ago, when Idina Menzel's version of the film's "Let It Go" -- the album's best-selling song with 606,000 downloads sold according to Nielsen SoundScan -- was officially serviced to adult contemporary radio stations by Disney.|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="smallsoundtrack">{{cite news|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/how-frozen-went-from-small-soundtrack-to-worldwide-phenomenon-20140311|title=How 'Frozen' Went From Small Soundtrack to Worldwide Phenomenon|quote=Yet Frozen took forever to develop – and that was part of Disney's marketing plan. A few weeks before the album made its debut last November 25th, the company's music division put out reliable pop star [[Demi_Lovato|Demi Lovato]]'s version of "Let It Go" – and it barely earned any radio play. But somewhere around early January, the album hit a tipping point, shortly after Disney began pushing the version by Idina Menzel, who plays Elsa in the animated film. "You don't really want to go out [first] with a clip of the film," says Ken Bunt, president of the Disney Music Group. "The idea was to go out with the Demi version and follow up with the Idina version. It's a non-traditional pop song for radio. We've been working it for a while, but radio is realizing, 'This is an undeniable song.'"|last=Knopper|first=Steve|date=March 11, 2014|newspaper=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|access-date=June 29, 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626032839/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/how-frozen-went-from-small-soundtrack-to-worldwide-phenomenon-20140311|archive-date=June 26, 2014}}</ref>。安德森-洛佩兹和洛佩兹还创作了由演员和歌手黛米·洛瓦托演唱的该歌曲的[[随它吧#黛米·洛瓦托版本|流行版本]]（歌词较短以及和声较轻），该版本在电影片尾字幕开始时播放。由于迪士尼音乐部门认为门泽尔的版本不是传统的流行歌曲，该部门曾计划在门泽尔的版本之前发行洛瓦托的版本<ref name="smallsoundtrack" />，歌曲的流行版本还单独发行了了一支音乐视频。

这首歌在商业上取得了成功，成为自1995年以来第一首来自迪士尼动画音乐的歌曲进入[[公告牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百强单曲榜]]前十位的歌曲，此前由[[凡妮莎·威廉姆斯|凡妮莎·威廉姆斯]]演唱的《[[风中奇缘_(电影)|风中奇缘]]》中的〈{{Le|风之彩|Colors of the Wind}}〉曾在该排行榜上排名第四。这首歌也是门泽尔第一首进入《公告牌》百强单曲榜前十位的单曲，使她成为第一位进入该榜单前十位的[[托尼奖|托尼奖]]表演奖得主<ref>{{cite news|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|title='Let It Go' Helps Idina Menzel Make Hot 100 History|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5937548/let-it-go-helps-idina-menzel-make-hot-100-history|access-date=March 16, 2014|newspaper=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|date=March 15, 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317234729/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5937548/let-it-go-helps-idina-menzel-make-hot-100-history|archive-date=March 17, 2014}}</ref>。这首歌是2014年美国第九大畅销歌曲，当年销量达到337万首<ref name="us sales 2014">{{cite web|title=It's Official: Pharrell Has 2014's Best-Selling Song|url=https://www.yahoo.com/music/its-official-pharrell-has-2014s-best-selling-106748836876.html|date=December 31, 2014|last=Grein|first=Paul|publisher=Yahoo! Music|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401070235/https://www.yahoo.com/music/its-official-pharrell-has-2014s-best-selling-106748836876.html|archive-date=April 1, 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>。截至2014年12月，歌曲在美国售出350万首<ref name="us_sales">{{cite web|title=The Big 9 in 2014: Disney|url=http://www.hitsdailydouble.com/news/newsPage.cgi?news10221m01|access-date=December 10, 2014|date=December 9, 2014|work=HITS Daily Double|publisher=HITS Digital Ventures}}</ref>。截至2014年3月12日，它是韩国所有原声带中最畅销的外国歌曲<ref name="Gaon Download Chart">{{cite web|title=Gaon Download Chart|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/digital_chart/download.php?nationGbn=E&current_year=&current_month=1&current_week=06&chart_Time=month|publisher=Gaon Chart|language=ko|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222063605/http://gaonchart.co.kr/digital_chart/download.php?nationGbn=E&current_year=&current_month=1&current_week=06&chart_Time=month|archive-date=February 22, 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>。

这首歌展现了被排斥的女王艾莎，当她被公众发现无法控制的产生冰的能力时，她放弃了自己的王国，来到高山之上，远离惊慌失措的市民，艾莎意识到她不再需要隐藏自己的超能力，因此告诉自己她不再受从小以来就不得不忍受的限制，她很高兴能够自由地使用她的超能力。如果没有这种障碍，她似乎可以更好地控制自己的超能力，为自己创造[[雪宝_(迪士尼)|一个活生生的雪人]]和一座宏伟的冰城堡。歌曲响起的同时她丢掉了一些东西，最值得注意的是她父母给她限制她超能力的手套，以及从她的头上拿下来扔在肩上的头饰，然后她解开了她的辫子发型。

〈随它吧〉在《公告牌》百强单曲榜上进入了前五位，并于2014年获得[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖]]、于2015年获得{{Le|格莱美奖最佳影视媒体作品歌曲|Grammy Award for Best Song Written for Visual Media}}奖项<ref name="ABC Grammys2">{{cite web|title=Show Bits: 'Frozen' Soundtrack Fires up With 2 Grammy Wins|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory/show-bits-frozen-soundtrack-fires-grammy-wins-28817993|access-date=February 9, 2015|publisher=ABC News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209035036/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory/show-bits-frozen-soundtrack-fires-grammy-wins-28817993|archive-date=February 9, 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>。这首歌曲获得了国际性的成功，成为全球录制最多的迪士尼歌曲之一，电影的国际发行版中共有41种不同语言的版本<ref>{{cite web|title=Hear Frozen's Let It Go Sung in 25 Different Languages|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Hear-Frozen-Let-It-Go-Sung-25-Different-Languages-41251.html|access-date=February 1, 2015|date=January 22, 2014|last=West|first=Kelly|publisher=CinemaBlend|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217033042/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Hear-Frozen-Let-It-Go-Sung-25-Different-Languages-41251.html|archive-date=February 17, 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>。

根据[[国际唱片业协会|国际唱片业协会]]的数据，〈随它吧〉在2014年卖出了1,090万首，成为当年第五大畅销歌曲<ref name="Ifpi20152">{{cite web|title=IFPI publishes Digital Music Report 2015|url=http://www.ifpi.org/news/Global-digital-music-revenues-match-physical-format-sales-for-first-time|access-date=April 15, 2015|date=April 14, 2015|publisher=International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414194629/http://www.ifpi.org/news/Global-digital-music-revenues-match-physical-format-sales-for-first-time|archive-date=April 14, 2015|page=12|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2014年5月19日，华特迪士尼唱片公司发行了一张[[混音|混音]][[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Caulfield|first1=Keith|title=Idina Menzel, 'Let It Go' (Papercha$er Club Remix): Exclusive Dance Track Premiere|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/code/5944616/idina-menzel-let-it-go-paperchaser-club-remix-exclusive-dance-track|access-date=June 11, 2014|work=Billboard|date=March 20, 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706020841/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/code/5944616/idina-menzel-let-it-go-paperchaser-club-remix-exclusive-dance-track|archive-date=July 6, 2014}}</ref>。该迷你专辑中收录了由Dave Audé、Papercha$er、DJ Escape & Tony Coluccio和Corbin Hayes混音的四首作品<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lansky|first1=Sam|title=Dave Audé Turns Frozen's "Let It Go" Into a Huge Dance Anthem: Listen|url=http://time.com/31707/let-it-go-frozen-dave-aude-remix/|access-date=June 11, 2014|work=Time|date=March 20, 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607121427/http://time.com/31707/let-it-go-frozen-dave-aude-remix/|archive-date=June 7, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Let It Go Remixes (From "Frozen") - EP by Idina Menzel|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/let-it-go-remixes-from-frozen/id875528297|access-date=September 19, 2014|date=May 19, 2014|publisher=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141206075452/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/let-it-go-remixes-from-frozen/id875528297|archive-date=December 6, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>。[[阿明·范·比伦|阿明·范·比伦]]为{{Le|混音专辑|Remix album}}《{{Le|Dconstructed}}》制作了这首歌的另一首混音<ref>{{cite news|last=Kennedy|first=Gerrick D.|title=Armin van Buuren, Avicii tapped for Disney remix album|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-armin-van-buuren-avicii-kaskade-tapped-for-disney-remix-album-20140312,0,4197447.story|access-date=April 19, 2014|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=March 12, 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419023359/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-armin-van-buuren-avicii-kaskade-tapped-for-disney-remix-album-20140312%2C0%2C4197447.story|archive-date=April 19, 2014}}</ref>。

==製作過程==
《随它吧》首先由[[克里斯汀·安德生-洛佩兹|克里斯汀·安德生-洛佩兹]]以及[[罗伯特·洛佩兹|罗伯特·洛佩兹]]為該部電影作曲。該團隊的靈感来源于迪士尼的其他電影，例如《[[小美人魚|小美人魚]]》以及《[[美女與野獸_(1991年電影)|美女與野獸]]》以及其他的歌手包括[[愛黛兒|愛黛兒]]，{{link-en|艾美·曼恩|Aimee Mann}}，[[女神卡卡|女神卡卡]]，[[艾薇兒·拉維尼|艾薇兒·拉維尼]]以及[[卡洛爾·金|卡洛爾·金]]。<ref>{{cite news|last=Willman|first=Chris|title=How the 'Frozen' Soundtrack Snowballed to No. 1|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/how-frozen-soundtrack-snowballed-no-670649?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+thr%2Fnews+(The+Hollywood+Reporter+-+Top+Stories)|accessdate=2014-01-20|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-01-15}}</ref>雖然這首歌是寫給該電影中的重要角色艾莎女王，然而一開始該角色是一個反派。導演[[克里斯·巴克|克里斯·巴克]]與[[珍妮佛·李|珍妮佛·李]]後來將艾莎改寫成正派主角。<ref name=EW1>{{cite news|last=Busis|first=Hillary|title=Disney's 'Frozen': Composers talk unexpected influences（Gaga!）and accidentally aping 'Arrested Development'|url=http://family-room.ew.com/2013/11/27/frozen-composers-bobby-lopez-kristen-anderson-lopez/|accessdate=2013-12-02|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly|date=2013-11-27|archive-date=2013-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131201015119/http://family-room.ew.com/2013/11/27/frozen-composers-bobby-lopez-kristen-anderson-lopez/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NYP/>

《随它吧》的主曲調為[[降A大調|降A大調]]；然而這首歌一開始是[[F小調|F小調]]，一直到[[伊迪娜·曼佐|伊迪娜·曼佐]]開始第二個段（“Don't let them in, don't let them see”）轉成降E[[Mixolydian調|Mixolydian調]]。最後經過簡短的轉調，除了橋段部分主旋律發展回原來的降A大調，而橋段則是用降D[[Mixolydian調|Mixolydian調]]以及降E [[Mixolydian調|Mixolydian調]]。這首歌的速度為四，每分鐘137拍。歌手Menzel的聲域在F<sub>3</sub>（低音Fa）到E♭<sub>5</sub>（高音Mi降半音）。

作詞作曲者安德森-羅培茲以及羅培茲特別為[[伊迪娜·曼佐|伊迪娜·曼佐]]寫出這首歌，考量到她是「[[百老匯劇院|百老匯劇院]]」中擁有最壯麗的聲音之一，以及音樂劇當中深具特色」，在作曲的過程中，也考量過她的音域下製作本歌。<ref name=WSJ>{{cite news|last=Chai|first=Barbara|script-title=en:Listen to Songs From Disney’s ‘Frozen’ and Hear How They Were Written|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2013/11/27/listen-to-songs-from-disneys-frozen-and-hear-how-they-were-written/|accessdate=2013-12-02|newspaper=The Wall Street Journal|date=2013-11-27|archive-date=2013-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204131653/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2013/11/27/listen-to-songs-from-disneys-frozen-and-hear-how-they-were-written/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==評論==
《随它吧》收到了來自世界各地的電影評論者，音樂評論者和觀眾的熱烈好評。不過有人拿來與{{link-en|Defying Gravity|Defying Gravity (song)}}做比較（同樣也是由Menzel演唱）。<ref name=NYP>{{cite news|last=Miller|first=Gregory E.|script-title=en:‘Frozen’ soundtrack set to join the ranks of Disney greats|url=http://nypost.com/2013/11/23/frozen-soundtrack-set-to-join-the-ranks-of-disney-greats/|accessdate=2013-12-02|newspaper=The New York Post|date=2013-11-23|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202084328/http://nypost.com/2013/11/23/frozen-soundtrack-set-to-join-the-ranks-of-disney-greats/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Rochester/><ref name=EW2/> {{link-en|羅切斯特市報|The Rochester City Newspaper}}稱其為最好的原聲帶歌曲，並表示：「[[伊迪娜·曼佐|伊迪娜·曼佐]]唱得有聲有色，這首歌擁有讓人長期喜愛的各項元素……曼佐應該展現了如同她在《[[女巫前傳_(音樂劇)|女巫前傳]]》當中同樣的力道以及熱情。」<ref name=Rochester>{{cite news|last=DeTruck|first=Matt|title=CD Review: Disney's "Frozen" Soundtrack|url=http://www.rochestercitynewspaper.com/rochester/cd-review-disneys-frozen-soundtrack/Content?oid=2302643|accessdate=2013-12-02|newspaper=City Newspaper|date=2013-11-27|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203023510/http://www.rochestercitynewspaper.com/rochester/cd-review-disneys-frozen-soundtrack/Content?oid=2302643|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]的Marc Snetiker描述本首歌為「不可思議的解放之頌」（an incredible anthem of liberation）<ref name=EW2>{{cite news|last=Sneitker|first=Marc|title=Disney's 'Frozen' soundtrack: Ranking all nine original songs|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/11/30/disney-frozen-soundtrack-ranking/|accessdate=2013-12-02|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly|date=2013-11-30|archive-date=2013-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131209024514/http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/11/30/disney-frozen-soundtrack-ranking/|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]的Joe Dziemianowicz則稱其為「a stirring tribute to girl power and the need to 'let go' of fear and shame」。<ref name=NY>{{cite news|last=Dziemianowicz|first=Joe|title=Disney's 'Frozen' scores a show-stopping song with Idina Menzel's 'Let It Go'|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/grabbing-year-hot-show-tume-article-1.1538652|accessdate=2013-12-08|newspaper=[[纽约日报|纽约日报]]|date=2013-12-06|archive-date=2014-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114042532/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/grabbing-year-hot-show-tume-article-1.1538652|dead-url=no}}</ref>

